ComicInfo.Summary:
Skye Mathers, along with Julia, the Queen of Hearts, has been making her way back to her home world, one universal leap at a time. But her journey has just taken a seriously wrong turn, separating her from her partner. And these new surroundings Skye finds herself in could signal dire consequences for the future she is hurtling toward. What horrible truths lie in this place? Who is the Keeper? And where is Julia?
Don’t miss this all new chapter in Skye’s adventure, sure to answer many questions and create some new ones, as well!
